headline: Federal Realty Sells Misora at Santana Row as Part of Ongoing Capital Recycling Program
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) today announced the sale of Misora Apartments, a 212-unit Class A residential community at Santana Row in San Jose, California, for $148.5 million.

headline: UDR Set to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in Store for the Stock?
summary: UDR gears up to report Q4 results as revenues and FFO per share are expected to rise despite soft apartment demand and elevated supply.
